title: Building a Search App in React.js using Typesense, Next.js & Tailwind CSS

media:group.media:title: Building a Search App in React.js using Typesense, Next.js & Tailwind CSS
media:group.media:description:
Typesense is an open source, typo tolerant search engine that is optimised for instant sub-50ms searches, while providing an intuitive developer experience.

In this video we are going to build an instant search type applicaiton in React.js with Typesense as the search engine for searching through a collection of books. Our React.js will be set up using Next.js with TypeScript. For CSS we will be using Tailwind CSS.
